xwikidoc.title: Half-Orc Grog
xwikidoc.content: [[image:Grog.png||style="float: right;"]]Grog is a barbarian of questionable heritage, possible half-orc. He currently lives in Tisloch and is an associate of the dwarf [[ Gilladian>>DwarfGilladian]]. He claims to have come from [[Erklond>>Erklond]] and has adventured widely in various areas of Erithnoi. He makes his living as an adventurer, mercenary, and bodyguard. Grog is legendary for his dim wits and love of battle. In general he is good natured and tends to work for good employers, but with his feeble intellect he may well fall in with shady types. When not otherwise occupied he can be found spending his earnings in various gambling and drinking establishments around Tisloch. However as he has few attachments he might potentially be found wandering anywhere in western Erithnoi.
